data.text:
For a trainer without an Umamusume, the best course of action is 
to familiarize oneself with them in the meantime.

choices.text: (Time to give it my all observing today, too!)

data.text: Huff, huff, huff, huff...!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: <story>Huff, huff, huff, huff...!

data.text:
When I arrived at the training grounds, I saw Agnes Digital 
running on the dirt track.
data.processed:
<story>When I arrived at the training grounds, I saw Agnes Digital 
<story>running on the dirt track.

data.text:
She pushed against the dirt with impressive strength, despite 
her small size. 
In a mere flash, she was already rushing down the final straight.

choices.text: (She looks pretty used to it... Has she already debuted?)
choices.processed: <size=29>(She looks pretty used to it... Has she already debuted?)</size>

choices.text: (She looks pretty used to it... Has she already debuted?)

<story>her small size. 
<story>In a mere flash, she was already rushing down the final straight.

data.text: Whew...
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: <story>Whew...

data.text:
Good work, Agnes Digital-san! You were on point today too! 
Keep it up, and you're in good shape for the Selection Race!
data.name: Instructor
data.processed:
<story>Good work, Agnes Digital-san! You were on point today too! 
<story>Keep it up, and you're in good shape for the Selection Race!

data.text:
Huh...!? 
The... Selection Race...?
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>Huh...!? 
<story>The... Selection Race...?

data.text:
That's kind of... Er... 
Sorry, I need some time to think about it...
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>That's kind of... Er... 
<story>Sorry, I need some time to think about it...

data.text: A-Anyway, I'm off to the turf track now...!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: <story>A-Anyway, I'm off to the turf track now...!

data.text: Ah... right, see you later! Don't push yourself too hard, all right?
data.name: Instructor
data.processed: <story>Ah... right, see you later! Don't push yourself too hard, all right?

data.text: Training that hard on turf and dirt tracks every day? That's twice as much work as the other girls. ...It's really impressive.
data.name: Instructor
data.processed: Training that hard on turf and dirt tracks every day? That's twice as much work as the other girls. ...It's really impressive.

data.text:
This time, she took off onto the turf. I was taken aback by how 
nimbly she ran. Even though I was so sure that she'd specialized 
in running on dirt――
data.processed:
<story>This time, she took off onto the turf. I was taken aback by how 
<story>nimbly she ran. Even though I was so sure that she'd specialized 
<story>in running on dirt――

data.text:
I took her time with a stopwatch, just out of curiousity, and 
when I saw her time, my eyes went wide.
data.processed:
<story>I took her time with a stopwatch, just out of curiousity, and 
<story>when I saw her time, my eyes went wide.

data.text: She was a great runner on dirt and turf. But from what I overheard, she hadn't even run in the Selection Race, much less debuted.
data.processed: She was a great runner on dirt and turf. But from what I overheard, she hadn't even run in the Selection Race, much less debuted.

data.text:
I wanted to know what was going on, so I made my way down to 
the track to hear it from her.
data.processed:
<story>I wanted to know what was going on, so I made my way down to 
<story>the track to hear it from her.

data.text: Hoo-whee~.... As always, the track after Umamusume-chans finish running is just THE BEST!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: Hoo-whee~.... As always, the track after Umamusume-chans finish running is just THE BEST!

data.text: If I keep this up, I'll have the best seat in the house no matter what kind of race it is! Mufufu, there's my virtuous deed for the day!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: If I keep this up, I'll have the best seat in the house no matter what kind of race it is! Mufufu, there's my virtuous deed for the day!

data.text:
Oh, but that was cutting it pretty close... Almost went and signed 
up for the Selection Race. I'd never be able to live that down~.
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>Oh, but that was cutting it pretty close... Almost went and signed 
<story>up for the Selection Race. I'd never be able to live that down~.

data.text:
I wouldn't. I'm still mad at myself for almost making such a 
puffed-rice-brained decisio――
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>I wouldn't. I'm still mad at myself for almost making such a 
<story>puffed-rice-brained decisio――

data.text: ――Wait, HUH!? What...!? Whom...!?
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: ――Wait, HUH!? What...!? Whom...!?

data.text:
Oh, it's just you. The Umamusume-chan fan from the other day. 
Hello, hello~.
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>Oh, it's just you. The Umamusume-chan fan from the other day. 
<story>Hello, hello~.

data.text: So, how've you been? You been doing those virtuous deeds?
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: <story>So, how've you been? You been doing those virtuous deeds?

data.text: I'm still out here living my worshipful life. Saying grace to my faves. Giving thanks for the bounty of their moe. Sometimes I get so emotional I just start to cry――
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: I'm still out here living my worshipful life. Saying grace to my faves. Giving thanks for the bounty of their moe. Sometimes I get so emotional I just start to cry――

data.text:
――Wait, not now!! 
Did you. Hear that first bit...!?
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>――Wait, not now!! 
<story>Did you. Hear that first bit...!?

data.text: Ah. Knew it. So you heard me...
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: <story>Ah. Knew it. So you heard me...

data.text:
It shouldn't be too hard to explain, if you can bear with me going 
delulu about my faves...
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>It shouldn't be too hard to explain, if you can bear with me going 
<story>delulu about my faves...

data.text:
I just can't choose between turf and dirt. 
Sure, part of the problem comes from my 50-50 skillset, but――
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>I just can't choose between turf and dirt. 
<story>Sure, part of the problem comes from my 50-50 skillset, but――

data.text:
The real issue's that picking one means abandoning the other. 
I reeeeaaa――lly don't want to have to do that...
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>The real issue's that picking one means abandoning the other. 
<story>I reeeeaaa――lly don't want to have to do that...

data.text:
When it comes to Central races, the higher the grade, the more 
likely it'll be on turf. So the majority of Umamusume forgo dirt to 
get better at running on turf.
data.processed:
<story>When it comes to Central races, the higher the grade, the more 
<story>likely it'll be on turf. So the majority of Umamusume forgo dirt to 
<story>get better at running on turf.

data.text: Most Umamusume would just say "it is what it is", but she――
data.processed: <story>Most Umamusume would just say "it is what it is", but she――

data.text:
Yes, but of course! My love for Umamusume-chan knows not 
turf nor dirt! For all they are all my faves, and pwecious all the 
same!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>Yes, but of course! My love for Umamusume-chan knows not 
<story>turf nor dirt! For all they are all my faves, and pwecious all the 
<story>same!

data.text: What?
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: <story>What?

data.text:
No, yeah. That's the thing of it! 
They're all so pwecious I just can't choose!!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>No, yeah. That's the thing of it! 
<story>They're all so pwecious I just can't choose!!

data.text:
Yes, exactly! Surely a karmic veteran like you would understand! 
They're all pwecious!! BUT...!!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>Yes, exactly! Surely a karmic veteran like you would understand! 
<story>They're all pwecious!! BUT...!!

data.text: If I go for turf, I can't go see Umamusume-chans on dirt! If I go for dirt, I can't go see Umamusume-chans on turf!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: If I go for turf, I can't go see Umamusume-chans on dirt! If I go for dirt, I can't go see Umamusume-chans on turf!

data.text:
Ghaahhh, how is this even a thing? All because of this, I've said 
no to every scouting, every Selection Race!!!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>Ghaahhh, how is this even a thing? All because of this, I've said 
<story>no to every scouting, every Selection Race!!!

data.text: E・ven・though・I want to see aaaaaa――aaalll the Umamusume-chans up close, turf AND dirt!!!!
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: E・ven・though・I want to see aaaaaa――aaalll the Umamusume-chans up close, turf AND dirt!!!!

data.text:
...Somehow, I get the feeling we're having two very different 
conversations here.
data.processed:
<story>...Somehow, I get the feeling we're having two very different 
<story>conversations here.

data.text: You understand this pain, don't you!? Don't you, Umamusume-chan-loving trainer?
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: You understand this pain, don't you!? Don't you, Umamusume-chan-loving trainer?

data.text:
She was kind of talking up a storm, so I got her to stop for a 
second so I could figure things out...
data.processed:
<story>She was kind of talking up a storm, so I got her to stop for a 
<story>second so I could figure things out...

data.text:
She didn't want to give up on either dirt or turf Umamusume 
――her "faves". 
But if she wanted to debut, she'd have to pick one or the other.
data.processed:
<story>She didn't want to give up on either dirt or turf Umamusume 
<story>――her "faves". 
<story>But if she wanted to debut, she'd have to pick one or the other.

data.text:
But she couldn't make that choice, and ended up refusing 
everyone who tried to scout her... That's the gist of it.
data.processed:
<story>But she couldn't make that choice, and ended up refusing 
<story>everyone who tried to scout her... That's the gist of it.

data.text:
Ha... If it was more obvious which tracks I'm better at, that'd 
make things a whole lot easier to figure out...
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed:
<story>Ha... If it was more obvious which tracks I'm better at, that'd 
<story>make things a whole lot easier to figure out...

data.text:
She didn't have a good reason to choose one or the other. 
So maybe it'd be better to actually do something instead of 
just thinking about it. Maybe――
data.processed:
<story>She didn't have a good reason to choose one or the other. 
<story>So maybe it'd be better to actually do something instead of 
<story>just thinking about it. Maybe――

data.text: ...Huh? Them...?
data.name: Agnes Digital
data.processed: <story>...Huh? Them...?

Looking down at the track, it just so happened that T.M. Opera O, 
Overlord of Turf, and Smart Falcon, the Ruler of Dirt, were there.
data.processed:
<story>Looking down at the track, it just so happened that T.M. Opera O,

data.name: Agnes Digital

Ah, are the two of you... 
...Perhaps admirers of mine?

Very well then. If you want a photoshoot, a deep cut, an
